==In popular culture== * Codex Regius is the subject of a thriller by the Icelandic writer [[Arnaldur Indridason]]. * [[Werner Herzog]] reads aloud one poem in his 2016 film ''[[Into_the_Inferno_(film)|Into the Inferno]]''.
