{{Greeks}}
This is a list of Greek artists from the antiquity to today. Artists have been categorised according to their main artistic profession and according to the major historical period they lived in: the '''Ancient''' (until the foundation of the [[Byzantine Empire]]), the '''Byzantine''' (until the fall of [[Constantinople]] in 1453) and the '''Modern''' period (1453-today).
